node.text:
If you really think it's for the best... I would love to have it.

{{rules|Rofwufufuf runs on all fours to the great dragon. He immediately nips and licks Azhdahak's scaled ankles. Azhdahak exhales a puff of ethanol from his nostrils.}}

Thanksss, =name=. You have my eternal gratitude.

